Blue Circle Tracker
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Blue Circle Tracker is a simple program to track any blue circle in a video. 



Simple Appearance-Based Blob Tracking
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Simple Appearance-Based Blob Tracking is a short example of using SimpleCV. 
This example shows a simple idea on tracking multiple objects using an 
appearance model. The algorithm here can be improved by using a better 
appearance model or the Kalman filters.

